  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Previously untreated and histologically confirmed locoregionally advanced
             nasopharyngeal carcinoma

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  A history of another invasive cancer, prior RT to the head and neck area, prior
             cytotoxic chemotherapy or anti-EGFR therapy or the presence of any serious medical
             conditions, supposed to live less than 6 months.
      </textblock>
